       Apram inayaoda 7 months aguthu namba pesi enala atha nichyama namba mudiyala diii 💝🫂 
       Ipa varaikum na unkita irunthu nee enakita irunthum. Yarukumae theriyatha secrets kuda namba rendu perum share panirukum .... 😊
       Na avlo la intresting ana person ila  irunthalum nee still yen kita pesikitu Iruka atha ethaiyum ethir pakam so thanks ... 🫰
       Nee en life la Ethuku vantha yenn vantha ethuvumae enaku theriyathu ana you're best and loveable chapter of my life .... 😉
       Nee epayum ipa mari sirchikitae irukanum na God kita ketukren so smile and namba bond forever nu .....♾️</p>
